# No Parallel Execution

- Do not run commands in parallel in this project.
- Prefer sequential execution for shell commands, builds, generation, sync, validation, and any other execution work.
- Do not launch subagents in parallel if any of them performs execution or other non-readonly work.
- Only consider parallel work for clearly read-only inspection when there is no execution involved, and prefer sequential work by default.
